<P>THE <HI>ART</HI> OF SPEAKING.</P>
<P><HI>CONTAINING,</HI></P>
<P N="1">I. An ESSAY; in which are given Rules for expre&s;&s;ing properly the principal Pa&s;&s;ions and Humours, which occur in Reading, or public Speaking; and</P>
