<L>Thick <HI>light'nings fla&s;h;</HI> the <HI>mutt'ring thunder rolls;</HI></L>
<L>Their <HI>&s;trength</HI> he <HI>withers,</HI> and <HI>unmans</HI> their <HI>&s;ouls.</HI><NOTE PLACE="marg">Fear.</NOTE></L>
