<L><HI>Bear</HI> on your <HI>wings,</HI> and in your <HI>notes</HI> his <HI>prai&s;e<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">.</HI></L>
<L>Ye that in <HI>waters glide,</HI> and ye that <HI>walk</HI></L>
<L>The <HI>earth,</HI> and <HI>&s;tately tread,</HI> or <HI>lowly creep.</HI></L>
<L><HI>Witne&s;s,</HI> if I <HI>be &s;ilent, morn</HI> or <HI>ev'n,</HI></L>
<L>To <HI>hill,</HI> or <HI>valley, fountain,</HI> or <HI>fre&s;h &s;hade</HI></L>
