<L><HI>Hail univer&s;al Lord!</HI> Be <HI>bounteous</HI> &s;till,<NOTE PLACE="marg">Profound Submi&s;&s;ion.</NOTE></L>
<L>To <HI>give</HI> us <HI>only good;</HI> and if the <HI>night</HI></L>
<L>Have <HI>gather'd</HI> aught of <HI>evil,</HI> or <HI>conceal'd,</HI></L>
