<L><NOTE PLACE="marg">Concern.</NOTE>If <HI>parts</HI> allure thee, think how <HI>Bacon</HI> &s;hin'd,</L>
<L>The <HI>wi&s;e&s;t, brighte&s;t&mdash;meane&s;t</HI> of mankind:</L>
<L><NOTE PLACE="marg">Contempt. Aver&s;ion. Teaching.</NOTE>Or ravi&s;h'd with the <HI>whi&s;tling of a name,</HI></L>
