<DIV2 N="32" TYPE="lesson">
<HEAD>XXXII. SEEMING CIVILITY.</HEAD>
<ARGUMENT>
<P>The meeting between the knight of the Red Cro&s;&s;e, attended by Truth, with Hypocri&s;y.</P>
