</ARGUMENT>
<LG>
<L>AT length they chaun&s;t to <HI>meet</HI> upon the way</L>
<L>An <HI>aged &s;ire</HI><NOTE N="(2)" PLACE="foot">Hypocri&s;y.</NOTE> in <HI>long black weeds</HI> yclad,<NOTE PLACE="marg">De&s;cription.</NOTE> <NOTE N="(3)" PLACE="foot">Clothed.</NOTE></L>
<L>His <HI>feete</HI> all <HI>bare,</HI> his <HI>beard</HI> all <HI>hoarie grey,</HI></L>
