<L><PB N="120" REF="028373_0119_0FD8B1E6C0F1CA70"><HI>Bidding</HI> his <HI>beads</HI><NOTE N="(1)" PLACE="foot">Saying his prayers.</NOTE> all day for his tre&s;pas,</L>
