<L><PB N="121" REF="028373_0120_0FD8B1EC2CB16418"><HI>Untroubled night,</HI> they &s;ay, gives coun&s;el <HI>be&s;t.</HI>"</L>
<L>"<HI>Right well,</HI> Sir knight,<NOTE PLACE="marg">Inviting.</NOTE> ye have advi&s;ed bin,"</L>
<L>Quoth then that aged man; "The way to <HI>win</HI> <NOTE N="(1)" PLACE="foot">Conquer.</NOTE></L>
<L>Is <HI>wi&s;ely</HI> to <HI>advi&s;e;</HI> now <HI>day</HI> is <HI>&s;pent;</HI></L>
<L>Therefore with me you may take up your <HI>In</HI></L>
