<L><PB N="162" REF="028373_0161_0FD8B243149057E0"><HI>Brutus</HI> will <HI>&s;tart</HI> a <HI>gho&s;t</HI> as <HI>&s;oon</HI> as <HI>Cae&s;ar.</HI></L>
<L><NOTE PLACE="marg">Wonder.</NOTE>Now in the <HI>names</HI> of <HI>all</HI> the <HI>gods</HI> at <HI>once,</HI></L>
<L>Upon what <HI>meat</HI> doth this our <HI>Cae&s;ar</HI> feed,</L>
