<L><HI>Rome,</HI> thou ha&s;t <HI>lo&s;t</HI> the <HI>breed</HI> of <HI>noble bloods.</HI></L>
<L><HI>When</HI> went there by an age, &s;ince the <HI>&s;un &s;hone,</HI></L>
<L>But it was fam'd with more than <HI>one</HI> man?</L>
