<L>To claim our ju&s;t <HI>inheritance</HI> of <HI>old,</HI></L>
<L><HI>Surer</HI> to <HI>pro&s;per</HI> than <HI>pro&s;perity</HI></L>
<L><PB N="245" REF="028373_0244_0FD8B53FC143EDC8">Could have <HI>a&s;&s;ured</HI> us, and by what <HI>be&s;t way,</HI></L>
