</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Longh.</SPEAKER>
<P><HI>No.</HI><NOTE PLACE="marg">Vexation.</NOTE></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<PB N="272" REF="028373_0271_0FD88D3E65F83318">
<SPEAKER>Nev.</SPEAKER>
