</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Nev.</SPEAKER>
<P><NOTE PLACE="marg">Affect.</NOTE>If it has for its object the <HI>three opera|tions</HI> of the <HI>mind,</HI> or the <HI>third</HI> only.<NOTE PLACE="marg">Vexation.</NOTE></P>
