</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Longh.</SPEAKER>
<P><HI>No, no,</HI> it is <HI>quite another affair,</HI><NOTE PLACE="marg">Vexat.</NOTE> I tell you.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Nev.</SPEAKER>
<P>You mu&s;t <HI>explain your&s;elf,</HI> then;<NOTE PLACE="marg">Affect.</NOTE> for I have mentioned the mo&s;t <HI>difficult</HI> points, and tho&s;e, that are commonly <HI>agitated</HI> in the <HI>&s;chools</HI> in our times.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Longh.</SPEAKER>
<P>I &s;hould have <HI>told</HI> you my <HI>bu&s;ine&s;s</HI> an <HI>hour ago,</HI> if you would have <HI>heard</HI> me.<NOTE PLACE="marg">Vexat.</NOTE></P>
