<P>Do you think,<NOTE PLACE="marg">Anxiety.</NOTE> I &s;hould run the hazard of being a <HI>cuckold,</HI> if I &s;hould <HI>marry</HI> her?<NOTE PLACE="marg">Affect.</NOTE></P>
</SP>
<SP>
