<P>There is no <HI>natural impo&s;&s;ibility</HI> in it. But, if you &s;hould, you may, <HI>perhaps,</HI><NOTE PLACE="marg">Affect.</NOTE> <HI>not</HI> be the <HI>fir&s;t,</HI> nor the <HI>la&s;t.</HI> But <HI>all things</HI> are <HI>uncertain.</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
