<P>I'll <HI>make</HI> you <HI>change</HI> your <HI>cuckow-note,</HI> you old philo&s;ophical <HI>hu<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">dru<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">,</HI><NOTE PLACE="marg">Pa&s;&s;ion.</NOTE> you&mdash;
<STAGE>[beats him]</STAGE>
&mdash;I will&mdash;
<STAGE>[beats him]</STAGE>
I'll <HI>make</HI> you &s;ay <HI>&s;omewhat el&s;e,</HI> than "<HI>All things</HI> are <HI>doubtful; all things</HI> are <HI>uncertain</HI>"&mdash;
<STAGE>[beats him]</STAGE>
I <HI>will,</HI> you old <HI>fu&s;ty pedant.</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
