<P><HI>Ah!&mdash;oh!&mdash;eh!</HI><NOTE PLACE="marg">Compl.</NOTE>&mdash;What beat a <HI>philo&s;opher!&mdash;Ah!&mdash;oh!&mdash;eh!</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
